    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history available. You can expect a driving experience that feels brand new in every respect.",
