    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for its next owner. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in solid working order, providing a dependable driving experience. However, please note that there are visible signs of wear and tear, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable aging in the interior upholstery. It\u2019s a great option for someone looking for a functional vehicle at an affordable price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
      "price": 18500.0,
